    "description": "<p>PeopleSolve provides healthcare manpower solutions in Singapore, China, and internationally.&nbsp;</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>It offers permanent full time and part time healthcare staffing solutions; local and overseas hiring expertise; medical English and clinical training programs; and outsourcing solutions for nurses, allied health and healthcare HR teams.&nbsp;</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>The company provides a comprehensive range of service to support healthcare organizations of all sizes. Whether it's addressing nurses shortages or enhancing operational efficiency, PeopleSolve delivers customized services to contribute to the success of healthcare organizations globally.&nbsp;</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>The company was founded in 2021 and is headquartered in Singapore (21C0695).&nbsp;</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>For more information or inquiries, please contact us at: peoplesolve@peoplesolve.com.sg .&nbsp;</p>",
